Automation.help:
- This command supports Discord Markdown. (Chat formatting: bold, italics, underline, etc.)
- You can include the following in your message:
**{mention}** - Mentions the User;
**{user}** - Shows Username;
**{server}** - Shows server name;
**{membercount}** - Shows number of people in server;

